#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/attendance_logs.rst:3
msgid "Attendance logs"
msgstr "Fremmødelogfiler"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/attendance_logs.rst:5
msgid ""
"When entering the **Attendances** application, the :guilabel:`Overview` "
"dashboard is presented by default, and displays all the user's attendance "
"logs (their check in and check out information) for the current day. If the "
"user has the required :ref:`access rights <attendances/access-rights>` or is "
"an :ref:`approver <attendances/approvers>` for specific employees, those "
"employees' attendance logs also appear on the :guilabel:`Overview` dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Når man går ind i **Fremmøde**-applikationen, "
"præsenteres :guilabel:`Oversigt`-dashboardet som standard og viser alle "
"brugerens fremmødelogfiler (deres indtjekning og udtjekningsinformation) for "
"den aktuelle dag. Hvis brugeren har de krævede :ref:`adgangsrettigheder "
"<attendances/access-rights>` eller er en :ref:`godkender <attendances/"
"approvers>` for specifikke medarbejdere, vises disse medarbejderes "
"fremmødelogfiler også på :guilabel:`Oversigt`-dashboardet."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/attendance_logs.rst:11
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Overview` dashboard displays the current day, segmented by "
"hour, with the current hour highlighted in yellow. The appearance of "
"the :guilabel:`Overview` dashboard is determined by the :ref:`working "
"schedule <employees/schedule>` set on the employee's records. Each "
"employee's working hours appear in white, while all other hours appear in "
"gray. This allows managers to visually determine if an employee is working "
"outside of their working hours."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Oversigt`-dashboardet viser den aktuelle dag, opdelt efter time, "
"med den aktuelle time fremhævet i gult. Udseendet af :guilabel:`Oversigt`-"
"dashboardet bestemmes af den :ref:`arbejdsplan <employees/schedule>`, der er "
"angivet i medarbejderens poster. Hver medarbejders arbejdstimer vises i "
"hvidt, mens alle andre timer vises i gråt. Dette gør det muligt for ledere "
"visuelt at afgøre, om en medarbejder arbejder uden for deres arbejdstid."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/attendance_logs.rst:17
msgid ""
"Employees populate the rows, alphabetically by first name. Each attendance "
"log displays the total hours along with the specific check in and check out "
"times. The log colors indicate the following statuses:"
msgstr ""
"Medarbejdere udfylder rækkerne, alfabetisk efter fornavn. Hver "
"fremmøderegistrering viser det samlede antal timer sammen med de specifikke "
"check-ind- og check-ud-tidspunkter. Logfarverne angiver følgende statusser:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/attendance_logs.rst:21
msgid "Gray: Completed entries where the employee has checked in and out."
msgstr "Grå: Afsluttede poster, hvor medarbejderen har tjekket ind og ud."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/attendance_logs.rst:22
msgid ""
"Green: Active entries where the employee checked in but has not yet checked "
"out."
msgstr ""
"Grøn: Aktive poster, hvor medarbejderen har tjekket ind, men endnu ikke har "
"tjekket ud."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/attendance_logs.rst:23
msgid ""
"Red: Entries with any errors (e.g. employees have double entries, or forget "
"to check out)."
msgstr ""
"Rød: Poster med eventuelle fejl (f.eks. medarbejdere har dobbelte poster "
"eller glemmer at tjekke ud)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/attendance_logs.rst:None
msgid ""
"The overview dashboard presenting the information for the week, with the "
"current day\n"
"highlighted."
msgstr ""
"Oversigts-dashboardet præsenterer informationen for ugen med den aktuelle "
"dag\n"
"fremhævet."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/attendance_logs.rst:29
msgid ""
"A color-coded bar indicates how many hours out of the total expected hours "
"the employee has logged for the day. Rollover the color bar to view the "
"details for the employee's current day. Solid colors indicate the logged "
"hours (with both a start and end time), while pale colors indicate the "
"employee is signed in, but has not signed out yet. Only *completed* "
"attendance logs (records with a check in and check out time) appear in the "
"summary of the logged time."
msgstr ""
"En farvekodet bjælke angiver, hvor mange timer ud af de samlede forventede "
"timer medarbejderen har logget for dagen. Hold musen over farvebjælken for "
"at se detaljerne for medarbejderens aktuelle dag. Ensartede farver angiver "
"de loggede timer (med både start- og sluttidspunkt), mens blege farver "
"angiver, at medarbejderen er logget ind, men endnu ikke har logget ud. Kun "
"*afsluttede* fremmøderegistreringer (poster med et check-ind- og check-ud-"
"tidspunkt) vises i oversigten over den loggede tid."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/attendance_logs.rst:36
msgid ""
"Abigail Peterson is scheduled to work from 9:00 AM to 12:00 PM, then take a "
"one-hour lunch break from 12:00 PM to 1:00 PM, then work from 1:00 PM to "
"6:00 PM, for a total of eight hours."
msgstr ""
"Abigail Peterson er planlagt til at arbejde fra kl. 9:00 til kl. 12:00, "
"derefter holde en times frokostpause fra kl. 12:00 til kl. 13:00 og derefter "
"arbejde fra kl. 13:00 til kl. 18:00, i alt otte timer."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/attendance_logs.rst:39
msgid ""
"Abigails checks in at 9:00 AM, and checks out at 12:00 PM. She logs in again "
"at 1:00 PM. The current time is 2:15 PM. The rollover information displays "
"`3h / 8h`, indicating Abigail has logged three completed working hours out "
"of a total of eight. There is a pale green line that extends past the "
"summary block, indicating she checked in at 1:00 PM, but has not yet checked "
"out. The length of the pale green line indicates the time worked."
msgstr ""
"Abigail tjekker ind kl. 9:00 og tjekker ud kl. 12:00. Hun logger ind igen "
"kl. 13:00. Det aktuelle tidspunkt er kl. 14:15. Rulleoveroplysningerne viser "
"`3t / 8t`, hvilket angiver, at Abigail har logget tre afsluttede "
"arbejdstimer ud af i alt otte. Der er en bleg grøn linje, der strækker sig "
"forbi oversigtsblokken, hvilket angiver, at hun tjekkede ind kl. 13:00, men "
"endnu ikke har tjekket ud. Længden af den blege grønne linje angiver den "
"arbejdede tid."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/attendance_logs.rst:0
msgid ""
"The rollover green bar indicating Abigail logged 3 hours, and is currently "
"logged in."
msgstr ""
"Den grønne rulleoverbjælke angiver, at Abigail har logget 3 timer og aktuelt "
"er logget ind."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/attendance_logs.rst:48
msgid ""
"The **Attendances** dashboard allows for changing the displayed time period, "
"either :guilabel:`Day`, :guilabel:`Week`, :guilabel:`Month`, :guilabel:`Quarter`, :guilabel:`Year`, "
"or a custom time period. To instantly return the dashboard to the present "
"date, click the :guilabel:`Today` button at any time."
msgstr ""
"Dashboardet **Fremmøde** giver mulighed for at ændre den viste tidsperiode, "
"enten :guilabel:`Dag`, :guilabel:`Uge`, :guilabel:`Måned`, :guilabel:`Kvartal`, :guilabel:`År` "
"eller en brugerdefineret tidsperiode. For øjeblikkeligt at returnere "
"dashboardet til den aktuelle dato skal du til enhver tid klikke på "
"knappen :guilabel:`I dag`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/attendance_logs.rst:54
msgid ""
"Any attendance logs that have errors appear in red, indicating they need to "
"be resolved by a user with the proper :ref:`access rights <attendances/"
"access-rights>` or are :ref:`approvers <attendances/approvers>` for the "
"employees with the errors."
msgstr ""
"Alle fremmøderegistreringer, der har fejl, vises med rødt, hvilket angiver, "
"at de skal løses af en bruger med de korrekte :ref:`adgangsrettigheder "
"<attendances/access-rights>` eller er :ref:`godkendere <attendances/"
"approvers>` for medarbejderne med fejlene."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/attendance_logs.rst:61
msgid "Filters and groups"
msgstr "Filtre og grupper"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/attendance_logs.rst:63
msgid ""
"Sometimes, attendance officers and managers need to view specific records, "
"such as all automatic checkouts, to determine which employees chronically "
"forget to check out, or by department, to determine which team is working "
"the most overtime."
msgstr ""
"Sommetider har fremmødekontrollanter og ledere brug for at se specifikke "
"registreringer, såsom alle automatiske udtjekninger, for at bestemme hvilke "
"medarbejdere kronisk glemmer at stemple ud, eller efter afdeling, for at "
"bestemme hvilket hold der arbejder mest overarbejde."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/attendance_logs.rst:67
msgid ""
"For these cases, use the search bar to select a :icon:`fa-"
"filter` :guilabel:`Filters` or :icon:`oi-group` :guilabel:`Group By`, or "
"combine both to present the desired information."
msgstr ""
"I disse tilfælde skal du bruge søgelinjen til at vælge en :icon:`fa-"
"filter` :guilabel:`Filtre` eller :icon:`oi-group` :guilabel:`Gruppér efter`, "
"eller kombinere begge for at præsentere de ønskede oplysninger."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/attendance_logs.rst:74
msgid "High-value filters"
msgstr "Højværdi-filtre"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/attendance_logs.rst:81
msgid "Filter"
msgstr "Filter"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/attendance_logs.rst:82
msgid "Common use case"
msgstr "Almindelig brugssituation"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/attendance_logs.rst:83
msgid "At Work"
msgstr "På arbejde"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/attendance_logs.rst:84
msgid ""
"Verify employees still on-site before shutting down the building for the "
"night, or to perform a head count."
msgstr ""
"Verificer medarbejdere, der stadig er på stedet, før bygningen lukkes for "
"natten, eller for at udføre en hovedoptælling."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/attendance_logs.rst:86
#: ../../content/applications/hr/lunch/orders.rst:115
msgid "Errors"
msgstr "Fejl"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/attendance_logs.rst:87
msgid "View all errors to correct them prior to payroll processing."
msgstr "Se alle fejl for at rette dem inden lønbehandling."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/attendance_logs.rst:88
msgid "Automatically Checked-Out"
msgstr "Automatisk udtjekning"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/attendance_logs.rst:89
msgid ""
"Perform an audit to determine employees who chronically forget to check-out "
"of work."
msgstr ""
"Udfør en revision for at finde medarbejdere, der kronisk glemmer at tjekke "
"ud af arbejdet."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/attendance_logs.rst:90
msgid "Date"
msgstr "Dato"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/attendance_logs.rst:91
msgid "Limit results to a specific pay-period or audit window."
