#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/commissions.rst:4
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:381
msgid "Commissions"
msgstr "Provisioner"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/commissions.rst:6
msgid ""
"Commissions are payments made to employees that are earned as part of their "
"salary. The payments are awarded after a sale has been made, and the amount "
"depends on how much the sale was. Typically the amount is either a "
"percentage of the sale, or a set commission based on a structure created by "
"the company."
msgstr ""
"Provisioner er betalinger til medarbejdere, der optjenes som en del af deres "
"løn. Betalingerne tildeles efter et salg er gennemført, og beløbetafhænger "
"af, hvor meget salget var på. Typisk er beløbet enten en procentdel af "
"salget eller en fast provision baseret på en struktur, som virksomheden har "
"oprettet."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/commissions.rst:11
msgid ""
"To pay an employee a commission they earned, a separate commission paycheck "
"must be issued to the employee. In Odoo, a commission payslip is referred to "
"as a *warrant payslip*."
msgstr ""
"For at betale en medarbejder en provision, de har optjent, skal der udstedes "
"en separat provisionslønseddel til medarbejderen. I Odoo omtales en "
"provisionslønseddel som en *warrant-lønseddel*."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/commissions.rst:15
msgid "Create warrant payslips"
msgstr "Opret warrant-lønsedler"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/commissions.rst:17
msgid ""
"Warrant payslips are generated directly from the :guilabel:`Payslips "
"Batches` dashboard, which is accessed by navigating "
"to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> Payslips --> Batches`."
msgstr ""
"Warrant-lønsedler genereres direkte fra :guilabel:`Lønseddelbatches`-"
"dashboardet, som tilgås ved at navigere til :menuselection:`Løn-app --> "
"Lønsedler --> Batches`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/commissions.rst:20
msgid ""
"First, click the :guilabel:`Generate Warrant Payslips` button in the top-"
"left corner. Doing so reveals a :guilabel:`Generate Warrant Payslips` pop-up "
"window, in which the necessary information **must** be filled out."
msgstr ""
"Klik først på knappen :guilabel:`Generer warrant-lønsedler` i øverste "
"venstre hjørne. Dette viser et pop op-vindue :guilabel:`Generer warrant-"
"lønsedler`, hvor de nødvendige oplysninger **skal** udfyldes."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/commissions.rst:24
msgid ""
"Set the time frame the commission was earned, in the two fields next "
"to :guilabel:`Period`. Click into each field, and a calendar pop-up window "
"loads. Navigate to the desired date and click on it to select it."
msgstr ""
"Angiv tidsrammen, hvor provisionen blev optjent, i de to felter ved siden "
"af :guilabel:`Periode`. Klik i hvert felt, og et kalender pop op-vindue "
"indlæses. Naviger til den ønskede dato, og klik på den for at vælge den."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/commissions.rst:28
msgid ""
"Using the drop-down menu, select the :guilabel:`Department` in the "
"corresponding field. When a department is selected, the employees listed for "
"that department appear in the :guilabel:`Employee` section, below."
msgstr ""
"Vælg :guilabel:`Afdeling` i det tilsvarende felt ved hjælp af rullemenuen. "
"Når en afdeling vælges, vises medarbejderne på listen for den pågældende "
"afdeling i afsnittet :guilabel:`Medarbejder` nedenfor."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/commissions.rst:32
msgid ""
"If a file is needed for the record, upload a file to the :guilabel:`Import "
"File` field, such as a sales invoice, using the :guilabel:`Upload your file` "
"button. Any file type is accepted."
msgstr ""
"Hvis en fil er nødvendig til registreringen, skal du uploade en fil til "
"feltet :guilabel:`Importér fil`, f.eks. en salgsfaktura, ved hjælp af "
"knappen :guilabel:`Upload din fil`. Alle filtyper accepteres."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/commissions.rst:35
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Employee` section, enter the "
"individual :guilabel:`Commission Amount` for each employee in the far-right "
"column. To remove an employee, click the :icon:`fa-trash-"
"o` :guilabel:`(trash)` icon to remove the line."
msgstr ""
"Under afsnittet :guilabel:`Medarbejder` skal du indtaste det "
"individuelle :guilabel:`Provisionsbeløb` for hver medarbejder i kolonnen "
"yderst til højre. For at fjerne en medarbejder skal du klikke på "
"ikonet :icon:`fa-trash-o` :guilabel:`(papirkurv)` for at fjerne linjen."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/commissions.rst:39
msgid ""
"Add a new commission by clicking :guilabel:`Add a Line`, and entering "
"the :guilabel:`Employee` and the appropriate :guilabel:`Commission Amount`."
msgstr ""
"Tilføj en ny provision ved at klikke på :guilabel:`Tilføj en linje` og "
"indtaste :guilabel:`Medarbejder` og det passende :guilabel:`Provisionsbeløb`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/commissions.rst:42
msgid ""
"Once all the commissions are properly entered, click the :guilabel:`Generate "
"Payslips` button to create the warrant payslips in a group, which is "
"reffered to as a *pay run* in Odoo, or click :guilabel:`Export` to export a "
"CSV file of the commissions."
msgstr ""
"Når alle provisioner er korrekt indtastet, klik på "
"knappen :guilabel:`Generer lønsedler` for at oprette warrantlønsedler i en "
"gruppe, hvilket i Odoo kaldes en *lønkørsel*, eller klik "
"på :guilabel:`Eksporter` for at eksportere en CSV-fil med provisionerne."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/commissions.rst:46
msgid ""
":ref:`Process the pay run <payroll/pay-run-process>` in the same way as a "
"typical batch to complete the payment process."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Behandl lønkørslen <payroll/pay-run-process>` på samme måde som en "
"typisk batch for at fuldføre betalingsprocessen."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/commissions.rst:None
msgid "Enter the commission details."
msgstr "Indtast provisionsdetaljerne."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/commissions.rst:53
msgid ":doc:`Commissions <../../sales/sales/commissions>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Provisioner <../../sales/sales/commissions>`"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:5
msgid ""
"Every employee in Odoo is required to have a running contract in order to be "
"paid. A contract outlines the terms of an employee's position, compensation, "
"working hours, and any other relevant terms."
msgstr ""
"Hver medarbejder i Odoo skal have en løbende kontrakt for at kunne modtage "
"løn. En kontrakt beskriver vilkårene for en medarbejders stilling, "
"kompensation, arbejdstider og andre relevante vilkår."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:9
msgid ""
"Contracts are created and managed in the *Payroll* tab of an :ref:`employee "
"record <employees/payroll>`. Employee records can be found by navigating "
"to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> Employees --> Employees`, or on the main "
"dashboard of the **Employees** app."
msgstr ""
"Kontrakter oprettes og administreres i fanen *Løn* i "
"en :ref:`medarbejderpost <employees/payroll>`. Medarbejderposter kan findes "
"ved at navigere til :menuselection:`Løn-app --> Medarbejdere --> "
"Medarbejdere` eller på hoveddasboardet i **Medarbejdere**-appen."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:14
msgid ""
"Contract documents (PDFs) are uploaded and organized using the **Documents** "
"application, and are signed using the **Sign** application. Ensure these "
"applications are installed to send and sign contracts. Please refer to "
"the :doc:`../../productivity/documents` and :doc:`../../productivity/sign` "
"documentation for more information."
msgstr ""
"Kontraktdokumenter (PDF'er) uploades og organiseres ved hjælp af "
"**Dokumenter**-applikationen og underskrives ved hjælp af **Underskriv**-"
"applikationen. Sørg for, at disse applikationer er installeret for at sende "
"og underskrive kontrakter. Se :doc:`../../productivity/documents` "
"og :doc:`../../productivity/sign` dokumentationen for mere information."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:22
msgid "Create a contract"
msgstr "Opret en kontrakt"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:24
msgid ""
"Contracts are created by uploading a :ref:`contract template <payroll/"
"contract-template>` and making any necessary modifications for the specific "
"employee. Contract templates eliminate the need to configure new contracts "
"every time an employee is hired."
msgstr ""
"Kontrakter oprettes ved at uploade en :ref:`kontraktskabelon <payroll/"
"contract-template>` og foretage eventuelle nødvendige ændringer for den "
"specifikke medarbejder. Kontraktskabeloner eliminerer behovet for at "
"konfigurere nye kontrakter hver gang en medarbejder ansættes."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:28
msgid ""
"Contract templates are created through the configuration menu of the "
"**Payroll** or **Employees** apps and stored in the **Documents** app. If no "
"contract templates exist, or if a new contract template is "
"needed, :ref:`create a new template <payroll/contract-template>`."
msgstr ""
"Kontraktskabeloner oprettes gennem konfigurationsmenuen i **Løn**- eller "
"**Medarbejdere**-apps og gemmes i **Dokumenter**-appen. Hvis der ikke findes "
"kontraktskabeloner, eller hvis der er brug for en ny "
"kontraktskabelon, :ref:`opret en ny skabelon <payroll/contract-template>`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:32
msgid ""
"Having multiple contract templates allows for faster contract creation for "
"commonly filled employment positions, such as full time, part time, "
"seasonal, etc."
msgstr ""
"At have flere kontraktskabeloner giver mulighed for hurtigere "
"kontraktoprettelse til almindeligt besatte stillinger såsom fuldtid, deltid, "
"sæson osv."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:35
msgid ""
"To create a new contract from a template, open the employee record and click "
"into the *Payroll* tab. Click :guilabel:`Load a Template`, and a *Contract "
"Template Load* pop-up window appears."
msgstr ""
"For at oprette en ny kontrakt fra en skabelon skal du åbne medarbejderposten "
"og klikke ind i fanen *Løn*. Klik på :guilabel:`Indlæs en skabelon`, og et "
"pop op-vindue *Kontraktskabelon indlæsning* vises."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:38
msgid ""
"Using the drop-down menu, select the contract template for the employee, "
"then click :guilabel:`Load`. The various fields from the template populate "
"the corresponding fields in the *Payroll* tab, and the updates are recorded "
"in the chatter. Additional sections may appear, depending on the contract "
"template. Then, make any required modifications to the fields in the various "
"sections of the *Payroll* tab."
msgstr ""
"Vælg kontraktskabelonen for medarbejderen ved hjælp af rullemenuen, og klik "
"derefter på :guilabel:`Indlæs`. De forskellige felter fra skabelonen "
"udfylder de tilsvarende felter i fanen *Løn*, og opdateringerne registreres "
"i chatteren. Yderligere afsnit kan vises afhængigt af kontraktskabelonen. "
"Foretag derefter eventuelle nødvendige ændringer i felterne i de forskellige "
"afsnit i fanen *Løn*."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:45
msgid ""
"To access contract templates, the **Salary Configurator** "
"(`hr_contract_salary`) module **must** be :ref:`installed <general/"
"install>`. Depending on the installed :doc:`payroll localization "
"<payroll_localizations>`, different sections and fields may appear in the "
"*Payroll* tab."
msgstr ""
"For at få adgang til kontraktskabeloner **skal** modulet **Salary "
"Configurator** (`hr_contract_salary`) være :ref:`installeret <general/"
"install>`. Afhængigt af den installerede :doc:`lønlokalisering "
"<payroll_localizations>` kan forskellige afsnit og felter vises i fanen "
"*Løn*."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:52
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:92
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:253
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:370
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:109
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/mexico.rst:134
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:106
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:88
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_states.rst:136
msgid "Contract overview section"
msgstr "Oversigtssektion for kontrakt"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:54
msgid ""
"The only field *not* modified after loading a :ref:`contract template "
"<payroll/contract-template>` is the :guilabel:`Contract` field. This field "
"specifies the start date of the contract."
msgstr ""
"Det eneste felt, der *ikke* ændres efter indlæsning af "
"en :ref:`kontraktskabelon <payroll/contract-template>`, er "
"feltet :guilabel:`Kontrakt`. Dette felt angiver startdatoen for kontrakten."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:57
msgid ""
"Click into the :guilabel:`Contract` field to reveal a calendar selector. "
"Click the start date for the contract. Once a date is selected, "
"a :guilabel:`to` field appears next to the start date. By "
"default, :guilabel:`Indefinite` is displayed in gray, indicating the "
"contract does not expire. If there is a set end date for the contract, click "
"into the :guilabel:`Indefinite` field, and click on the contract end date to "
"select it."
msgstr ""
"Klik ind i feltet :guilabel:`Kontrakt` for at få vist en kalendervælger. "
"Klik på startdatoen for kontrakten. Når en dato er valgt, vises "
"et :guilabel:`til`-felt ved siden af startdatoen. Som standard "
"vises :guilabel:`Ubestemt` med gråt, hvilket indikerer, at kontrakten ikke "
"udløber. Hvis der er en fastsat slutdato for kontrakten, skal du klikke ind "
"i feltet :guilabel:`Ubestemt` og klikke på kontraktens slutdato for at vælge "
"den."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:64
msgid ""
"This field may remain blank if a start date is not known. Once the contract "
"is signed, that date is set as the :guilabel:`Start Date`."
msgstr ""
"Dette felt kan forblive tomt, hvis en startdato ikke er kendt. Når "
"kontrakten er underskrevet, sættes den dato som :guilabel:`Startdato`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:70
msgid "Create contract templates"
msgstr "Opret kontraktskabeloner"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:72
msgid ""
"To create a new contract template, navigate to :menuselection:`Payroll app --"
"> Configuration --> Templates`, or :menuselection:`Employees app --> "
"Configuration --> Contract Templates`. Both methods open the *Contract "
"Templates* dashboard."
msgstr ""
"For at oprette en ny kontraktskabelon skal du navigere "
"til :menuselection:`Løn --> Konfiguration --> Skabeloner` "
"eller :menuselection:`Medarbejdere --> Konfiguration --> "
"Kontraktskabeloner`. Begge metoder åbner *Kontraktskabeloner*-dashboardet."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:76
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`New` button, and a blank contract template form loads. "
"Configure the following fields in the various sections of the form:"
msgstr ""
"Klik på knappen :guilabel:`Ny`, så indlæses en tom kontraktskabelonformular. "
"Konfigurer følgende felter i de forskellige sektioner af formularen:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:80
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/work_entries.rst:252
#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:35
msgid "General information section"
msgstr "Sektion for generelle oplysninger"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:82
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Template Name`: Enter a brief descriptive name for the template. "
"This should be clear and easily understood, as this name appears in the "
"**Recruitment** application, as well."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Skabelonnavn`: Indtast et kort beskrivende navn til skabelonen. "
"Dette navn bør være tydeligt og let forståeligt, da det også vises i "
"**Ansættelse**-applikationen."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:84
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Job`: Select the :doc:`job position <../recruitment/new_job>` the "
"contract template applies to from the drop-down menu. If blank, the template "
"applies to all job positions."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Job`: Vælg den :doc:`jobstilling <../recruitment/new_job>`, som "
"kontraktskabelonen gælder for, fra rullemenuen. Hvis feltet er tomt, gælder "
"skabelonen for alle jobstillinger."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:86
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Department`: Select the department the contract template applies "
"to from the drop-down menu. If blank, the template applies to all "
"departments."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Afdeling`: Vælg den afdeling, som kontraktskabelonen gælder for, "
"i rullemenuen. Hvis feltet er tomt, gælder skabelonen for alle afdelinger."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:88
msgid ""
":guilabel:`HR Responsible`: Select the employee responsible for validating "
"contracts, using this template, using the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`HR-ansvarlig`: Vælg den medarbejder, der er ansvarlig for at "
"validere kontrakter ved brug af denne skabelon, fra rullemenuen."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:94
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Wage Type`: Select either :guilabel:`Fixed Wage` "
"or :guilabel:`Hourly Wage` from the drop-down menu. Select :guilabel:`Fixed "
"Wage` for salaried employees, and select :guilabel:`Hourly Wage` for "
"employees who are paid based on their logged work hours."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Løntype`: Vælg enten :guilabel:`Fast løn` "
"eller :guilabel:`Timeløn` fra rullemenuen. Vælg :guilabel:`Fast løn` for "
"funktionærer, og vælg :guilabel:`Timeløn` for medarbejdere, der aflonnes på "
"baggrund af deres registrerede arbejdstimer."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:97
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Pay Schedule`: Using the drop-down menu, select how often the "
"employee is paid. The default options are: :guilabel:`year`, :guilabel:`half-"
"year`, :guilabel:`quarter`, :guilabel:`2 "
"months`, :guilabel:`month`, :guilabel:`half-month`, :guilabel:`2 "
"weeks`, :guilabel:`week`, or :guilabel:`day`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Udbetalingsplan`: Vælg fra rullemenuen, hvor ofte medarbejderen "
"får løn. Standardmulighederne "
"er: :guilabel:`år`, :guilabel:`halvår`, :guilabel:`kvartal`, :guilabel:`2 "
"måneder`, :guilabel:`måned`, :guilabel:`halv måned`, :guilabel:`2 "
"uger`, :guilabel:`uge` eller :guilabel:`dag`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:101
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Wage`: Enter the gross wage. The time period presented in this "
"field  reflects what is selected for the :guilabel:`Pay Schedule` field."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Løn`: Indtast bruttolønnen. Tidsperioden vist i dette felt "
"afspejler, hvad der er valgt i feltet :guilabel:`Udbetalingsplan`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:105
msgid ""
"It is recommended to populate the :guilabel:`Yearly Cost (Real)` field "
"*first*, since that value is used to automatically calculate "
"the :guilabel:`Wage`. If the :guilabel:`Yearly Cost (Real)` is updated, "
"the :guilabel:`Wage` field updates as well."
msgstr ""
"Det anbefales at udfylde feltet :guilabel:`Årlige omkostninger (faktiske)` "
"*først*, da denne værdi bruges til automatisk at beregne :guilabel:`Løn`. "
"Hvis :guilabel:`Årlige omkostninger (faktiske)` opdateres, opdateres "
"feltet :guilabel:`Løn` også."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:109
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Contract Type`: Using the drop-down menu, select one of the 18 "
"default types of contracts. This list is the same as the *employment type*."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kontrakttype`: Vælg en af de 18 standardkontrakttyper fra "
"rullemenuen. Denne liste er den samme som *ansættelsestypen*."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:111
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Pay Category`: Select one of the default pay categories using the "
"drop-down menu. The default pay categories are :guilabel:`Employee` "
"or :guilabel:`Worker`, which are pulled from the configured *salary "
"structures* in the **Payroll** app. A :ref:`new pay category <payroll/new-"
"structure-type>` can be created, if needed."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Lønkategori`: Vælg en af standardlønkategorierne fra rullemenuen. "
"Standardlønkategorierne er :guilabel:`Medarbejder` "
"eller :guilabel:`Arbejder`, som hentes fra de konfigurerede *lønstrukturer* "
"i **Løn**-appen. En :ref:`ny lønkategori <payroll/new-structure-type>` kan "
"oprettes, hvis nødvendigt."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:117
msgid ""
"In previous versions of Odoo, the :guilabel:`Pay category` was "
"called :guilabel:`Salary Structure Types`."
msgstr ""
"I tidligere versioner af Odoo blev :guilabel:`Lønkategori` "
"kaldt :guilabel:`Lønstrukturtyper`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:120
msgid ""
"To view, modify, or add pay categories, navigate to :menuselection:`Payroll "
"app --> Configuration --> Structure Types`."
msgstr ""
"For at se, ændre eller tilføje lønkategorier skal du navigere "
"til :menuselection:`Løn --> Konfiguration --> Strukturtyper`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:123
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Pay Category` drop-down menu displays all the available "
"working schedules. To modify or add to this list, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> Configuration --> Working Schedules`. "
"Click :guilabel:`New`, and create a new working schedule, or click on an "
"existing working schedule and make edits."
msgstr ""
"Rullemenuen :guilabel:`Lønkategori` viser alle tilgængelige arbejdsplaner. "
"For at ændre eller tilføje til denne liste skal du navigere "
"til :menuselection:`Løn --> Konfiguration --> Arbejdsplaner`. Klik "
"på :guilabel:`Ny`, og opret en ny arbejdsplan, eller klik på en eksisterende "
"arbejdsplan og foretag ændringer."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:129
msgid "Employer costs section"
msgstr "Sektion for arbejdsgiverens omkostninger"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:131
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Yearly Cost`: Enter the total yearly cost the employee costs the "
"employer. When this value is entered, the :guilabel:`Monthly Cost` "
"and :guilabel:`Wage` fields are automatically updated."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Årlige omkostninger`: Indtast den samlede årlige omkostning, som "
"medarbejderen koster arbejdsgiveren. Når denne værdi indtastes, opdateres "
"felterne :guilabel:`Månedlige omkostninger` og :guilabel:`Løn` automatisk."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:134
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Monthly Cost`: This field is **not** editable. The value is "
"automatically populated after the :guilabel:`Yearly Cost (Real)` is entered."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Månedlige omkostninger`: Dette felt kan **ikke** redigeres. "
"Værdien udfyldes automatisk, efter at :guilabel:`Årlige omkostninger "
"(faktiske)` er indtastet."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:138
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Wage`, :guilabel:`Yearly Cost`, and :guilabel:`Monthly Cost` "
"fields are all linked. If any of these fields are updated, the other two "
"fields automatically update to reflect the change. It is best practice to "
"check these three fields if any modifications have been made, to ensure they "
"are accurate."
msgstr ""
"Felterne :guilabel:`Løn`, :guilabel:`Årlige omkostninger` "
"og :guilabel:`Månedlige omkostninger` er alle forbundne. Hvis et af disse "
"felter opdateres, opdateres de to andre felter automatisk for at afspejle "
"ændringen. Det er god praksis at kontrollere disse tre felter, hvis der er "
"foretaget ændringer, for at sikre, at de er korrekte."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:143
msgid ":guilabel:`Wage on Signature`: Enter the monthly wage in the field."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Løn ved underskrivelse`: Indtast månedslønnen i feltet."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:146
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:303
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:388
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:139
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/mexico.rst:167
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:134
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:121
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_states.rst:168
msgid "Schedule section"
msgstr "Plansektion"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:148
msgid ""
"Configure the following two fields in this section, to configure when the "
"employee is expected to work:"
msgstr ""
"Konfigurer følgende to felter i denne sektion for at angive, hvornår "
"medarbejderen forventes at arbejde:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:153
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Work Entry Source`: Using the drop-down menu, select how "
"the :doc:`work entries <work_entries>` are generated. This field is "
"**required**. The options are:"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Arbejdsinput-kilde`: Vælg i rullemenuen, "
"hvordan :doc:`arbejdsinput <work_entries>` genereres. Dette felt er "
"**påkrævet**. Mulighederne er:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:156
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Working Schedule`: Work entries are generated based on the "
"selected :guilabel:`Working Schedule`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Arbejdsplan`: Arbejdsposter genereres baseret på den "
"valgte :guilabel:`Arbejdsplan`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:158
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Attendances`: Work entries are generated based on the employee's "
"check-in records in the **Attendances** app. (This requires the "
"**Attendances** app to be installed)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Fremmøde`: Arbejdsposter genereres baseret på medarbejderens "
"indtjekningsregistreringer i **Fremmøde**-appen. (Dette kræver, at "
"**Fremmøde**-appen er installeret)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:160
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Planning`: Work entries are generated based on the planned "
"schedule for the employee from the **Planning** app. (This requires the "
"**Planning** app to be installed)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Planlægning`: Arbejdsposter genereres baseret på den planlagte "
"tidsplan for medarbejderen fra **Planlægning**-appen. (Dette kræver, at "
"**Planlægning**-appen er installeret)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:163
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Working Hours`: Select one of the available :guilabel:`Working "
"Hours` the employee is expected to work, using the drop-down menu. The "
"selected working hours determine how :doc:`work entries <work_entries>` are "
"generated, which determines the employees schedule and compensation. If this "
"field is left blank, the employee can work as many or as few hours as "
"desired each week, with no restrictions. The default options "
"are :guilabel:`Standard 40 hours/week`, and :guilabel:`Appointment Resource "
"Default Calendar`"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Arbejdstimer`: Vælg en af de "
"tilgængelige :guilabel:`Arbejdstimer`, som medarbejderen forventes at "
"arbejde, ved hjælp af rullemenuen. De valgte arbejdstimer bestemmer, "
"hvordan :doc:`arbejdsinput <work_entries>` genereres, hvilket afgør "
"medarbejderens tidsplan og kompensation. Hvis dette felt efterlades tomt, "
"kan medarbejderen arbejde så mange eller så få timer som ønsket hver uge "
"uden begrænsninger. Standardmulighederne er :guilabel:`Standard 40 timer/"
"uge` og :guilabel:`Aftaleressource standardkalender`"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:171
msgid ""
"In previous versions of Odoo, :guilabel:`Working Hours` were "
"called :guilabel:`Working Schedules`."
msgstr ""
"I tidligere versioner af Odoo blev :guilabel:`Arbejdstimer` "
"kaldt :guilabel:`Arbejdsskemaer`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:175
msgid "Benefits and deductions"
msgstr "Ydelser og fradrag"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:177
msgid ""
"Depending on the :doc:`payroll localization <payroll_localizations>` for the "
"company, the remaining sections either vary, or may not appear at all. For "
"example, some entries may pertain to retirement accounts, health insurance "
"benefits, and commuter benefits."
msgstr ""
"Afhængigt af :doc:`lønlokaliseringen <payroll_localizations>` for "
"virksomheden varierer de resterende sektioner, eller vises måske slet ikke. "
"Nogle poster kan for eksempel vedrøre pensionskonti, "
"sundhedsforsikringsydelser og pendlerydelser."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:181
msgid ""
"Enter the monetary amounts or percentages to specify how much of the "
"employee's salary goes to the various benefits and deductions."
msgstr ""
"Angiv de monetære beløb eller procentsatser for at specificere, hvor meget "
"af medarbejderens løn der går til de forskellige ydelser og fradrag."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:185
msgid "Signatories tab"
msgstr "Fanen underskrivere"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:187
msgid ""
"This tab outlines which contract template to use when creating a new "
"contract for an employee, and which to use when updating an existing "
"contract. This section also outlines which signatures are required.  "
"Configure the following fields:"
msgstr ""
"Denne fane beskriver, hvilken kontraktskabelon der skal bruges ved "
"oprettelse af en ny kontrakt for en medarbejder, og hvilken der skal bruges "
"ved opdatering af en eksisterende kontrakt. Denne sektion beskriver også, "
"hvilke underskrifter der er påkrævet. Konfigurer følgende felter:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:191
msgid ""
"New Contract :guilabel:`PDF Template`: Select the default PDF that a new "
"employee has to sign to accept an offer."
msgstr ""
"Ny kontrakt :guilabel:`PDF-skabelon`: Vælg standard-PDF'en, som en ny "
"medarbejder skal underskrive for at acceptere et tilbud."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:193
msgid ""
"Contract Update :guilabel:`PDF Template`: Select the default PDF that a "
"current employee has to sign to update their contract."
msgstr ""
"Kontraktopdatering :guilabel:`PDF-skabelon`: Vælg standard-PDF'en, som en "
"nuværende medarbejder skal underskrive for at opdatere sin kontrakt."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:196
msgid "Once a PDF contract is uploaded, the following fields appear:"
msgstr "Når en PDF-kontrakt er uploadet, vises følgende felter:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:198
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Contract Role`: The label of the signature field to be signed. "
"This field is configured on the PDF itself, through the **Sign** app, and "
"cannot be modified."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kontraktrolle`: Etiketten på underskriftsfeltet, der skal "
"underskrives. Dette felt konfigureres på selve PDF'en gennem **Underskriv**-"
"appen og kan ikke ændres."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:200
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Signatory`: Using the drop-down menu, select the person who must "
"sign for the :guilabel:`Contract Role`. The default options are:"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Underskriver`: Vælg i rullemenuen den person, der skal "
"underskrive for :guilabel:`Kontraktrollen`. Standardmulighederne er:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:203
msgid ":guilabel:`Employee`: Select this for the employee to sign the field."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Medarbejder`: Vælg dette for at medarbejderen skal underskrive "
"feltet."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:204
msgid ""
":guilabel:`HR Responsible`: Select this to specify the user listed as "
"the :guilabel:`HR Responsible` on the job position."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`HR-ansvarlig`: Vælg dette for at angive den bruger, der er opført "
"som :guilabel:`HR-ansvarlig` på jobstillingen."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:206
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Specific Partner`: Select this to have a specific individual sign "
"the contract. When selected, the :guilabel:`Partner` field becomes active. "
"Using the drop-down menu, select the specific user who must sign the "
"contract in the :guilabel:`Partner` field."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Specifik partner`: Vælg dette for at lade en specifik person "
"underskrive kontrakten. Når dette vælges, bliver feltet :guilabel:`Partner` "
"aktivt. Vælg i rullemenuen den specifikke bruger, der skal underskrive "
"kontrakten i feltet :guilabel:`Partner`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:211
msgid ":doc:`../../productivity/documents`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../productivity/documents`"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:212
msgid ":doc:`../../productivity/sign`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../productivity/sign`"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:3
msgid "Headcount report"
msgstr "Medarbejdertalsrapport"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:5
msgid ""
"The *Headcount report* in the **Payroll** app shows the number of employees "
"on payroll and allows headcount comparisons between different periods of "
"time."
msgstr ""
"*Medarbejdertalsrapporten* i **Løn**-appen viser antallet af medarbejdere på "
"lønningslisten og giver mulighed for sammenligninger af medarbejdertal "
"mellem forskellige tidsperioder."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:9
msgid "Create a headcount report"
msgstr "Opret en medarbejdertalrapport"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:11
msgid ""
"Create a headcount report to see the number of employees at a specific time "
"or compare headcounts across periods."
msgstr ""
"Opret en medarbejdertalrapport for at se antallet af medarbejdere på et "
"bestemt tidspunkt eller sammenligne medarbejdertal på tværs af perioder."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:14
msgid ""
"To create a headcount report, navigate to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> "
"Reporting --> Headcount` and click :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"For at oprette en medarbejdertalrapport skal du navigere "
"til :menuselection:`Løn-app --> Rapportering --> Medarbejdertal` og klikke "
"på :guilabel:`Ny`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:17
msgid ""
"Report name: generated automatically as `Headcount for (Company Name) on the "
"(YYYY-MM-DD)` and **cannot** be modified."
msgstr ""
"Rapportnavn: genereres automatisk som `Medarbejdertal for (Virksomhedsnavn) "
"den (ÅÅÅÅ-MM-DD)` og **kan ikke** ændres."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:19
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Company`: populated automatically (works in both single and multi-"
"company databases)"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Virksomhed`: udfyldes automatisk (fungerer i både enkelt- og "
"multi-virksomhedsdatabaser)"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:20
msgid ""
":guilabel:`From`/:guilabel:`To` dates: defaults to current date (from) and "
"blank (to). Adjust these to define the period to analyze."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Fra`/:guilabel:`Til` datoer: standardindstillet til dags dato "
"(fra) og blank (til). Juster disse for at definere perioden, der skal "
"analyseres."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:None
msgid "A headcount report form filled out for the third quarter of 2025."
msgstr "En medarbejdertalrapportformular udfyldt for tredje kvartal af 2025."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:26
msgid "Next, click :guilabel:`Populate` to generate the report."
msgstr "Klik derefter på :guilabel:`Udfyld` for at generere rapporten."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:28
msgid ""
"At the top of the form, a :icon:`fa-people` :guilabel:`Employees` smart "
"button appears. Clicking the button displays the total number of employees "
"for the selected period."
msgstr ""
"Øverst på formularen vises en :icon:`fa-people` :guilabel:`Medarbejdere` "
"smart-knap. Ved at klikke på knappen vises det samlede antal medarbejdere "
"for den valgte periode."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:32
msgid "View all headcount reports"
msgstr "Vis alle medarbejdertalrapporter"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:34
msgid ""
"See how the company headcount has changed over time by viewing all headcount "
"reports in a list view."
msgstr ""
"Se hvordan virksomhedens medarbejdertal har ændret sig over tid ved at se "
"alle medarbejdertalrapporter i en listevisning."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:36
msgid ""
"To view all headcount reports, navigate to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> "
"Reporting --> Headcount`."
msgstr ""
"For at se alle medarbejdertalrapporter skal du navigere "
"til :menuselection:`Løn-app --> Rapportering --> Medarbejdertal`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:39
msgid "View employees in a headcount"
msgstr "Vis medarbejdere i et medarbejdertal"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:41
msgid ""
"TO get an overall view of employees and their salary impact on the company, "
"view all employee records of a specific headcount report."
msgstr ""
"For at få et samlet overblik over medarbejdere og deres lønpåvirkning på "
"virksomheden skal du se alle medarbejderposter for en bestemt "
"medarbejdertalrapport."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:44
msgid ""
"To view the employees of a specific headcount report, click the :icon:`fa-"
"people` :guilabel:`Employees` smart button at the top of a headcount report."
msgstr ""
"For at se medarbejderne i en bestemt medarbejdertalrapport skal du klikke "
"på :icon:`fa-people` :guilabel:`Medarbejdere` smart-knappen øverst på en "
"medarbejdertalrapport."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:47
msgid ""
"All employees from the headcount appear in a list view, grouped "
"by :guilabel:`Department`."
msgstr ""
"Alle medarbejdere fra medarbejdertallet vises i en listevisning, grupperet "
"efter :guilabel:`Afdeling`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:49
msgid ":guilabel:`Employee`: the employee's full name"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Medarbejder`: medarbejderens fulde navn"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:50
msgid ":guilabel:`Department`: the department their job position is in"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Afdeling`: den afdeling, deres jobstilling tilhører"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:51
msgid ":guilabel:`Job Title`: their role"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Jobtitel`: deres rolle"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:52
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Employer Cost`: how much the company pays the employee each pay-"
"period"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Arbejdsgiverens omkostning`: hvor meget virksomheden betaler "
"medarbejderen hver lønperiode"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:53
msgid ":guilabel:`Wage on Payroll`: the dollar amount on payroll reports"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Løn på lønningsliste`: beløbet i dollar på lønrapporter"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:3
msgid "Pay runs"
msgstr "Lønkørsler"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:5
msgid ""
"*Pay runs* are used to generate multiple :doc:`payslips <payslips>` at once "
"and process them in a group, rather than create and process individual "
"payslips. This method not only helps the payroll department pay employees in "
"less time, but it also helps keep payslips organized."
msgstr ""
"*Lønkørsler* bruges til at generere flere :doc:`lønsedler <payslips>` på én "
"gang og behandle dem i en gruppe, i stedet for at oprette og behandle "
"individuelle lønsedler. Denne metode hjælper ikke kun lønafdelingen med at "
"betale medarbejdere på kortere tid, men den hjælper også med at holde "
"lønsedler organiseret."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:9
msgid ""
"Typically, a company's payroll department :ref:`creates a new pay run "
"<payroll/new-pay-run>` for each salary structure, for every pay period "
"(usually weekly, bi-weekly, or monthly). If desired, pay runs can be further "
"organized by department, job position, etc."
msgstr ""
"Typisk :ref:`opretter en virksomheds lønafdelingen en ny lønkørsel <payroll/"
"new-pay-run>` for hver lønstruktur, for hver lønperiode (normalt ugentligt, "
"hver anden uge eller månedligt). Hvis ønsket kan lønkørsler yderligere "
"organiseres efter afdeling, jobstilling osv."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:13
msgid ""
"Once a pay run is made, :ref:`payslips are added to the pay run <payroll/add-"
"payslips>`, then the pay run is processed, and employees are paid."
msgstr ""
"Når en lønkørsel er oprettet, :ref:`tilføjes lønsedler til lønkørslen "
"<payroll/add-payslips>`, derefter behandles lønkørslen, og medarbejderne "
"betales."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:17
msgid "View pay runs"
msgstr "Vis lønkørsler"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:19
msgid ""
"To view all the pay runs in the database, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> Payslips --> Pay Runs` to display all "
"payslip pay runs that have been created. These payslip pay runs are "
"displayed in a list view, grouped by :icon:`oi-group` :guilabel:`Status` "
"(either :guilabel:`Ready`, :guilabel:`Done`, or :guilabel:`Paid`), by "
"default."
msgstr ""
"For at se alle lønkørsler i databasen skal du navigere "
"til :menuselection:`Løn-app --> Lønsedler --> Lønkørsler` for at vise alle "
"lønseddelkørsler, der er blevet oprettet. Disse lønseddelkørsler vises i "
"listevisning, grupperet efter :icon:`oi-group` :guilabel:`Status` "
"(enten :guilabel:`Klar`, :guilabel:`Udført` eller :guilabel:`Betalt`) som "
"standard."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:24
msgid ""
"Each pay run displays the name, the dates it includes, the number of "
"payslips, and the total :guilabel:`employer cost`, :guilabel:`gross`, "
"and :guilabel:`net` amounts for all payslips."
msgstr ""
"Hver lønkørsel viser navnet, de datoer den omfatter, antallet af lønsedler "
"og de samlede :guilabel:`arbejdsgivergebyr`, :guilabel:`brutto` "
"og :guilabel:`netto` beløb for alle lønsedler."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:None
msgid "View displaying all pay runs created."
msgstr "Visning der viser alle oprettede lønkørsler."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:33
msgid "Create a new pay run"
msgstr "Opret en ny lønkørsel"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:35
msgid ""
"New pay runs can be created from the :ref:`Work Entry <payroll/work-entry-"
"pay-run>`, :ref:`Employee Payslips <payroll/payslips-pay-run>`, or :ref:`Pay "
"Runs <payroll/pay-runs-pay-run>` dashboards."
msgstr ""
"Nye lønkørsler kan oprettes fra :ref:`Arbejdspost <payroll/work-entry-pay-"
"run>`-, :ref:`Medarbejderlønsedler <payroll/payslips-pay-run>`- "
"eller :ref:`Lønkørsler <payroll/pay-runs-pay-run>`-dashboardene."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:41
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/work_entries.rst:24
msgid "Work entry dashboard"
msgstr "Dashboard pracovních záznamů"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:43
msgid ""
"To create a pay run from the work entry dashboard, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> Work Entries --> Work Entries`. The "
"current time period is displayed, with the current day highlighted in yellow."
msgstr ""
"For at oprette en lønkørsel fra arbejdspost-dashboardet skal du navigere "
"til :menuselection:`Løn-app --> Arbejdsposter --> Arbejdsposter`. Den "
"aktuelle tidsperiode vises med den aktuelle dag fremhævet med gult."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:47
msgid ""
"All employees appear in a default Gantt view, with all work entries "
"displayed. If necessary, navigate to the desired time period."
msgstr ""
"Alle medarbejdere vises i en standard Gantt-visning med alle arbejdsposter "
"vist. Naviger om nødvendigt til den ønskede tidsperiode."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:50
msgid ""
"Once all :ref:`missing work entries are added <payroll/new-work-entry>` and "
"all :ref:`conflicts are resolved <payroll/conflicts>`, click "
"the :guilabel:`Generate Pay Run` button. The pay run is created for all "
"employees, with a status of :guilabel:`Ready`."
msgstr ""
"Når alle :ref:`manglende arbejdsposter er tilføjet <payroll/new-work-"
"entry>`, og alle :ref:`konflikter er løst <payroll/conflicts>`, klik på "
"knappen :guilabel:`Generer lønkørsel`. Lønkørslen oprettes for alle "
"medarbejdere med status :guilabel:`Klar`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:None
msgid "The work entries dashboard with the GeneratePay Runs button visible."
msgstr "Arbejdsposter-dashboardet med knappen Generer lønkørsler synlig."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:60
msgid "Employee payslips dashboard"
msgstr "Dashboard for medarbejderlønsedler"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:62
msgid ""
"To create a pay run from the payslips dashboard, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> Payslips --> Payslips`. All payslips for "
"all employees are displayed in a default list view, in chronological order."
msgstr ""
"For at oprette en lønkørsel fra lønsedler-dashboardet skal du navigere "
"til :menuselection:`Løn-app --> Lønsedler --> Lønsedler`. Alle lønsedler for "
"alle medarbejdere vises i en standard listevisning i kronologisk rækkefølge."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:68
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Pay Run` button and a :guilabel:`New Pay Run` pop-up "
"window loads. Select the :guilabel:`Salary Structure` using the drop-down "
"menu. If no :guilabel:`Salary Structure` is selected, the pay run applies to "
"*all* salary structures. Next, select the :guilabel:`Pay Schedule`, which is "
"*how often* employees are paid. The default options "
"are :guilabel:`year`, :guilabel:`half-"
"year`, :guilabel:`quarter`, :guilabel:`2 "
"months`, :guilabel:`month`, :guilabel:`half-month`, :guilabel:`2 "
"weeks`, :guilabel:`week`, or :guilabel:`day`."
msgstr ""
"Klik på knappen :guilabel:`Pay Run`, og et pop-op-vindue :guilabel:`New Pay "
"Run` indlæses. Vælg :guilabel:`Salary Structure` ved hjælp af rullemenuen. "
"Hvis ingen :guilabel:`Salary Structure` er valgt, gælder lønkørslen for "
"*alle* lønstrukturer. Vælg derefter :guilabel:`Pay Schedule`, som angiver "
"*hvor ofte* medarbejdere får løn. Standardindstillingerne "
"er :guilabel:`year`, :guilabel:`half-"
"year`, :guilabel:`quarter`, :guilabel:`2 "
"months`, :guilabel:`month`, :guilabel:`half-month`, :guilabel:`2 "
"weeks`, :guilabel:`week` eller :guilabel:`day`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:75
msgid ""
"Last, using the calendar selector, set the first day the pay run covers in "
"the first blank :guilabel:`Period` field. The second field is automatically "
"populated based on the selection in the :guilabel:`Pay Schedule` field."
msgstr ""
"Indstil til sidst ved hjælp af kalendervælgeren den første dag, lønkørslen "
"dækker, i det første tomme felt :guilabel:`Period`. Det andet felt udfyldes "
"automatisk baseret på valget i feltet :guilabel:`Pay Schedule`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:80
msgid ""
"A company pays its employees every month. To configure the pay run for "
"November, the :guilabel:`Pay Schedule` is set to :guilabel:`month`, and the "
"first :guilabel:`Period` field is set to `Nov 1`. Once entered, the second "
"field is automatically populated with `Nov 30`."
msgstr ""
"En virksomhed betaler sine medarbejdere hver måned. For at konfigurere "
"lønkørslen for november sættes :guilabel:`Pay Schedule` "
"til :guilabel:`month`, og det første felt :guilabel:`Period` sættes til `Nov "
"1`. Når det er indtastet, udfyldes det andet felt automatisk med `Nov 30`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:0
msgid "A monthly pay run configured for November."
msgstr "En månedlig lønkørsel konfigureret for november."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:87
msgid ""
"When the :guilabel:`New Pay Run` pop-up window is configured, "
"click :guilabel:`Continue`, and the pop-up window changes to "
"a :guilabel:`Select Employees` window. All employees who match the "
"parameters set in the :guilabel:`New Pay Run` pop-up window appear in the "
"list. Select the desired employees to add to the pay run, or click the box "
"next to :guilabel:`Employees` to select *all* employees in the list."
msgstr ""
"Når pop-op-vinduet :guilabel:`New Pay Run` er konfigureret, klik "
"på :guilabel:`Continue`, og pop-op-vinduet ændres til et "
"vindue :guilabel:`Select Employees`. Alle medarbejdere, der matcher de "
"parametre, der er angivet i pop-op-vinduet :guilabel:`New Pay Run`, vises på "
"listen. Vælg de ønskede medarbejdere, der skal tilføjes til lønkørslen, "
"eller klik på boksen ved siden af :guilabel:`Employees` for at vælge *alle* "
"medarbejdere på listen."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:None
msgid "The pay run employee selection pop-up window."
msgstr "Pop-op-vinduet til valg af medarbejdere til lønkørsel."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:96
msgid ""
"Once all desired employees are selected, click :guilabel:`Select`. The pop-"
"up window closes, and the pay run appears on the screen."
msgstr ""
"Når alle ønskede medarbejdere er valgt, klik på :guilabel:`Select`. Pop-op-"
"vinduet lukkes, og lønkørslen vises på skærmen."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:102
msgid "Pay runs dashboard"
msgstr "Dashboard for lønkørsler"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:104
msgid ""
"To create a pay run from the pay runs dashboard, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> Payslips --> Pay Runs`. Click "
"the :guilabel:`New` button and a :guilabel:`New Pay Run` pop-up window loads."
msgstr ""
"For at oprette en lønkørsel fra dashboardet for lønkørsler skal du navigere "
"til :menuselection:`Payroll app --> Payslips --> Pay Runs`. Klik på "
"knappen :guilabel:`New`, og et pop-op-vindue :guilabel:`New Pay Run` "
"indlæses."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:108
msgid ""
"Follow the same directions as if creating a :ref:`pay run form the payslips "
"dashboard <payroll/new-pay-run-pop-up>`."
msgstr ""
"Følg de samme instruktioner som ved oprettelse af en :ref:`lønkørsel fra "
"dashboardet for lønsedler <payroll/new-pay-run-pop-up>`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:114
msgid "Add a payslips to a pay run"
msgstr "Tilføj lønsedler til en lønkørsel"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:116
msgid ""
"Once a :ref:`pay run has been created <payroll/new-pay-run>`, payslips are "
"added as part of the pay run creation. If needed, additional payslips can be "
"created individually, and added to a pay run after it has been created."
msgstr ""
"Når en :ref:`lønkørsel er blevet oprettet <payroll/new-pay-run>`, tilføjes "
"lønsedler som en del af oprettelsen af lønkørslen. Hvis det er nødvendigt, "
"kan yderligere lønsedler oprettes individuelt og tilføjes til en lønkørsel, "
"efter den er blevet oprettet."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:120
msgid ""
"To add a new payslip, navigate to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> Payslips --"
"> Payslips`. Click the :guilabel:`New Off-Cycle` button and a "
"blank :guilabel:`Employee Payslips` form loads. :ref:`Configure the payslip "
"form <payroll/new-payslip>`, and ensure the :guilabel:`Pay Run` field is "
"populated."
msgstr ""
"For at tilføje en ny lønseddel skal du navigere til :menuselection:`Payroll "
"app --> Payslips --> Payslips`. Klik på knappen :guilabel:`New Off-Cycle`, "
"og en tom formular :guilabel:`Employee Payslips` indlæses. :ref:`Konfigurer "
"lønseddelformularen <payroll/new-payslip>`, og sørg for at "
"feltet :guilabel:`Pay Run` er udfyldt."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:125
msgid ""
"Once the form is configured, click :guilabel:`Compute Sheet` to calculate "
"the payslip and add it to the selected pay run."
msgstr ""
"Når formularen er konfigureret, klik på :guilabel:`Compute Sheet` for at "
"beregne lønsedlen og tilføje den til den valgte lønkørsel."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:131
msgid "Process a pay run"
msgstr "Behandl en lønkørsel"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:133
msgid ""
"After a :ref:`pay run has been created <payroll/new-pay-run>`, and :ref:`all "
"required payslips have been added <payroll/add-payslips>`, the pay run must "
"then be processed, and employees paid."
msgstr ""
"Efter en :ref:`lønkørsel er blevet oprettet <payroll/new-pay-run>`, "
"og :ref:`alle nødvendige lønsedler er blevet tilføjet <payroll/add-"
"payslips>`, skal lønkørslen derefter behandles, og medarbejderne betales."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:136
msgid ""
"Open the desired pay run by navigating to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> "
"Payslips --> Pay Runs`, and clicking on the desired pay run."
msgstr ""
"Åbn den ønskede lønkørsel ved at navigere til :menuselection:`Payroll app --"
"> Payslips --> Pay Runs` og klikke på den ønskede lønkørsel."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:139
msgid ""
"For a pay run to be processed, it must have a status of :guilabel:`Ready`. "
"That means the pay run has been created and payslips have been added, but "
"the payslips have *not* been processed."
msgstr ""
"For at en lønkørsel kan behandles, skal den have status :guilabel:`Ready`. "
"Det betyder, at lønkørslen er blevet oprettet, og lønsedler er blevet "
"tilføjet, men lønsedlerne er *ikke* blevet behandlet."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:142
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Create Draft Entry` button, then click :guilabel:`OK` "
"in the :guilabel:`Confirmation` pop-up window to confirm and create a draft "
"of all the individual payslips in the pay run. After this occurs, the pay "
"run status changes to :guilabel:`Done`, and moves to the corresponding "
"grouping on the :guilabel:`Pay Runs` dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Klik på knappen :guilabel:`Create Draft Entry`, og klik derefter "
"på :guilabel:`OK` i pop-op-vinduet :guilabel:`Confirmation` for at bekræfte "
"og oprette et udkast til alle de enkelte lønsedler i lønkørslen. Når dette "
"sker, ændres lønkørslens status til :guilabel:`Done` og flyttes til den "
"tilsvarende gruppering på dashboardet :guilabel:`Pay Runs`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:148
msgid ""
"At any time, the pay run needs to be reverted back to a status "
"of :guilabel:`Ready`, click the :guilabel:`Revert` button. This action does "
"**not** remove any payslips that have already been added to the pay run, "
"instead, the status changes back to :guilabel:`Ready`."
msgstr ""
"Hvis lønkørslen på noget tidspunkt skal tilbageføres til "
"status :guilabel:`Ready`, klik på knappen :guilabel:`Revert`. Denne handling "
"fjerner **ikke** nogen lønsedler, der allerede er blevet tilføjet til "
"lønkørslen. I stedet ændres status tilbage til :guilabel:`Ready`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:152
msgid ""
"After any desired changes have been made, click :guilabel:`Create Draft "
"Entry` and the pay run status changes to :guilabel:`Done`."
msgstr ""
"Når alle ønskede ændringer er foretaget, klik på :guilabel:`Opret "
"kladdepost`, og lønkørselsstatussen ændres til :guilabel:`Udført`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:155
msgid ""
"It is important to note, that if any payslips in the pay run have a status "
"of :guilabel:`Paid`, the pay run **cannot** revert to a status "
"of :guilabel:`Ready`."
msgstr ""
"Det er vigtigt at bemærke, at hvis nogen lønsedler i lønkørslen har "
"status :guilabel:`Betalt`, kan lønkørslen **ikke** vende tilbage til "
"status :guilabel:`Klar`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:158
msgid ""
"Once the status has changed to :guilabel:`Done`, the payments must be logged "
"in the database. Click the :guilabel:`Payment Report` button, and a pop-up "
"window loads, where the payment report details are entered."
msgstr ""
"Når status er ændret til :guilabel:`Udført`, skal betalingerne registreres i "
"databasen. Klik på knappen :guilabel:`Betalingsrapport`, og et pop op-vindue "
"indlæses, hvor betalingsrapportens detaljer indtastes."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:162
msgid ""
"Using the drop-down menu, select the :guilabel:`Export Format` for the "
"payment report. The universal option is :guilabel:`CSV`, while all other "
"available options depend on the installed :doc:`payroll localization "
"<payroll_localizations>`."
msgstr ""
"Brug rullemenuen til at vælge :guilabel:`Eksportformat` for "
"betalingsrapporten. Den universelle mulighed er :guilabel:`CSV`, mens alle "
"andre tilgængelige muligheder afhænger af den "
"installerede :doc:`lønlokaliseringen <payroll_localizations>`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:166
msgid ""
"Next, select the :guilabel:`Payment Date` using the calendar selector. This "
"is the date the paychecks are issued."
msgstr ""
"Vælg derefter :guilabel:`Betalingsdato` ved hjælp af kalendervælgeren. Dette "
"er datoen, hvor lønsedlerne udstedes."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:169
msgid ""
"Some :doc:`payroll localizations <payroll_localizations>` cause "
"a :guilabel:`Bank Journal` field to also appear. If visible, select the "
"journal the payslips are logged on, using the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"Nogle :doc:`lønlokalisationer <payroll_localizations>` medfører, at et "
"felt :guilabel:`Bankjournal` også vises. Hvis synligt, vælg den journal som "
"lønsedlerne registreres på ved hjælp af rullemenuen."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:172
msgid ""
"Once the pop-up window is configured, click the :guilabel:`Generate` button. "
"The :guilabel:`Payment Report` button changes to a :icon:`fa-"
"download` :guilabel:`Download (filetype)` button. To save a copy of the "
"payment report, click the :icon:`fa-download` :guilabel:`Download "
"(filetype)` button, select the location for the file, then "
"click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Når pop op-vinduet er konfigureret, klik på knappen :guilabel:`Generer`. "
"Knappen :guilabel:`Betalingsrapport` ændres til en :icon:`fa-"
"download` :guilabel:`Download (filtype)`-knap. For at gemme en kopi af "
"betalingsrapporten, klik på :icon:`fa-download` :guilabel:`Download "
"(filtype)`-knappen, vælg placeringen for filen og klik derefter "
"på :guilabel:`Gem`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:178
msgid ""
"If the screen is enlarged beyond a certain amount, the :icon:`fa-"
"download` :guilabel:`Download (filetype)` button is hidden from view. In "
"this scenario, click the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(vertical "
"ellipsis)` icon to view and select the :icon:`fa-"
"download` :guilabel:`Download (filetype)` option."
msgstr ""
"Hvis skærmen forstørres ud over en vis mængde, er :icon:`fa-"
"download` :guilabel:`Download (filtype)`-knappen skjult. I dette scenarie "
"skal du klikke på :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(lodret ellipse)`-ikonet "
"for at se og vælge :icon:`fa-download` :guilabel:`Download (filtype)`-"
"muligheden."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:183
msgid ""
"After the report is created, click the :guilabel:`Mark as paid` button to "
"mark the payslips as paid in the database."
msgstr ""
"Når rapporten er oprettet, skal du klikke på knappen :guilabel:`Marker som "
"betalt` for at markere lønsedlerne som betalt i databasen."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:187
msgid ""
"Odoo automatically creates the name of the pay run according to the various "
"selections made when creating the pay run (salary structure, pay schedule, "
"etc). In some situations, a company may want to rename the pay runs, for "
"better organization and a clearer understanding of what pay slips are part "
"of each pay run."
msgstr ""
"Odoo opretter automatisk navnet på lønkørslen i henhold til de forskellige "
"valg, der er foretaget ved oprettelse af lønkørslen (lønstruktur, "
"betalingsplan osv.). I nogle situationer kan en virksomhed ønske at omdøbe "
"lønkørslerne for bedre organisering og en klarere forståelse af, hvilke "
"lønsedler der er en del af hver lønkørsel."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:192
msgid ""
"For example, a company pays its employees monthly, for both hourly and "
"salaried employees."
msgstr ""
"For eksempel betaler en virksomhed sine medarbejdere månedligt, både "
"timelønnede og fastlønnede medarbejdere."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:194
msgid "The names for their four August 2025 pay runs are:"
msgstr "Navnene på deres fire lønkørsler i august 2025 er:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:196
msgid "`Aug 1-14 2025 - Hourly`"
msgstr "`1.-14. aug. 2025 - Timelønnede`"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:197
msgid "`Aug 1-14 2025 - Salary`"
msgstr "`1.-14. aug. 2025 - Fastlønnede`"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:198
msgid "`Aug 15-31 2025 - Hourly`"
msgstr "`15.-31. aug. 2025 - Timelønnede`"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:199
msgid "`Aug 15-31 2025 - Salary`"
msgstr "`15.-31. aug. 2025 - Fastlønnede`"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:3
msgid "Payroll analysis"
msgstr "Lønanalyse"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:5
msgid ""
"The *Payroll Analysis* report displays the total net wage for the company, "
"for the last 365 days. This report allows companies to view their payroll "
"costs and identify any trends."
msgstr ""
"Rapporten *Lønanalyse* viser den samlede nettoløn for virksomheden for de "
"sidste 365 dage. Denne rapport giver virksomheder mulighed for at se deres "
"lønomkostninger og identificere eventuelle tendenser."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:8
msgid ""
"To view the *Payroll Analysis* report, navigate to :menuselection:`Payroll "
"app --> Reporting --> Payroll`."
msgstr ""
"Pro zobrazení přehledu *Analýza mezd* přejděte na :menuselection:`aplikace "
"Løn --> Reporting --> Løn`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:11
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Net Wage` is the default metric displayed in the report, but "
"other measures can be displayed if desired, such as *gross wage* or *days of "
"paid time off*. Click the :guilabel:`Measures` :icon:`fa-caret-down` button "
"to view a drop-down menu of other metrics to display. Click on the desired "
"measure to display the results."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Nettoløn` je výchozí metrika zobrazená v přehledu, ale v případě "
"potřeby lze zobrazit další metriky, jako například *bruttoløn* nebo *dage "
"med betalt fri*. Klikněte na tlačítko :guilabel:`Metriky` :icon:`fa-caret-"
"down`, čímž zobrazíte rozbalovací nabídku s dalšími metrikami. Klikněte na "
"požadovanou metriku pro zobrazení výsledků."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:None
msgid "Payroll overview report showing payroll for the last 365 days."
msgstr "Lønoversigtsrapport, der viser løn for de sidste 365 dage."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:22
msgid "View multiple metrics"
msgstr "Zobrazit více metrik"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:24
msgid ""
"It is possible to view multiple metrics at one time by viewing the report in "
"the *pivot table* view. This can aid management to determine other trends, "
"such as which departments do not take time off, or which departments have "
"the highest payroll costs."
msgstr ""
"Je možné zobrazit více metrik najednou zobrazením přehledu v *pivottabel*. "
"To může pomoci vedení určit další trendy, například které afdelinger "
"nečerpají fri, nebo které afdelinger mají nejvyšší lønomkostninger."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:29
msgid ""
"**Only one** measure is able to be displayed in the default :icon:`fa-area-"
"chart` :guilabel:`Graph` view. Multiple measures are **only** possible in "
"the :icon:`oi-view-pivot` :guilabel:`Pivot` view."
msgstr ""
"**Pouze jednu** metriku lze zobrazit ve výchozím zobrazení :icon:`fa-area-"
"chart` :guilabel:`Graf`. Více metrik je možných **pouze** v "
"zobrazení :icon:`oi-view-pivot` :guilabel:`Pivot`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:33
msgid ""
"To display the data in a pivot table, click on the :icon:`oi-view-"
"pivot` :guilabel:`Pivot` button."
msgstr ""
"Pro zobrazení dat v pivottabelu klikněte na tlačítko :icon:`oi-view-"
"pivot` :guilabel:`Pivot`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:35
msgid ""
"The default information displayed includes the number of payslips "
"(:guilabel:`# Payslip`), the number of :guilabel:`Days of Paid Time Off` "
"and :guilabel:`Days of Unpaid Time Off`, along with the :guilabel:`Net Wage` "
"and :guilabel:`Gross Wage`. All the information is organized by department."
msgstr ""
"Výchozí zobrazené informace zahrnují počet lønsedler (:guilabel:`# "
"Lønseddel`), počet :guilabel:`Dage med betalt fri` a :guilabel:`Dage med "
"ubetalt fri` spolu s :guilabel:`Nettoløn` a :guilabel:`Bruttoløn`. Všechny "
"informace jsou uspořádány podle afdelinger."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:39
msgid ""
"To display more information on the report, click "
"the :guilabel:`Measures` :icon:`fa-caret-down` button to reveal a drop-down "
"menu. Click on any metric to display it on the pivot table."
msgstr ""
"Pro zobrazení více informací v přehledu klikněte na "
"tlačítko :guilabel:`Metriky` :icon:`fa-caret-down`, čímž zobrazíte "
"rozbalovací nabídku. Klikněte na libovolnou metriku pro její zobrazení v "
"pivottabelu."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:None
msgid "Pivot table view with the various metrics on display."
msgstr "Zobrazení pivottabelu s různými zobrazenými metrikami."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:46
msgid "Use case: comparing payroll costs"
msgstr "Případ použití: porovnání lønomkostninger"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:48
msgid ""
"Managers can compare payroll costs, and determine which departments have "
"raised their payroll costs, either by hiring more employees, or by raising "
"salaries."
msgstr ""
"Vedoucí mohou porovnat lønomkostninger a určit, které afdelinger zvýšily své "
"lønomkostninger, buď přijetím více medarbejdere, nebo zvýšením platů."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:51
msgid ""
"To compare previous periods of time, first view the *Payroll Analysis* "
"report in a :ref:`pivot table <payroll_analysis/multiple>`. Then, click "
"the :icon:`fa-caret-down` :guilabel:`(Toggle Search Panel)` icon in the "
"search bar, and click  :guilabel:`Start Date` :icon:`fa-caret-down` to "
"reveal a list of time periods (months, quarters, and years). Click on a "
"desired time period, and a :icon:`fa-adjust` :guilabel:`Comparison` section "
"appears in the search bar. Click on one of the two available options, "
"either :guilabel:`Start Date: Previous Period`, or :guilabel:`Start Date: "
"Previous Year`."
msgstr ""
"Pro porovnání předchozích časových období nejprve zobrazte přehled *Analýza "
"mezd* v :ref:`pivottabelu <payroll_analysis/multiple>`. Poté klikněte na "
"ikonu :icon:`fa-caret-down` :guilabel:`(Přepnout panel vyhledávání)` ve "
"vyhledávacím řádku a klikněte na :guilabel:`Startdato` :icon:`fa-caret-"
"down`, čímž zobrazíte seznam časových období (měsíce, čtvrtletí a roky). "
"Klikněte na požadované časové období a ve vyhledávacím řádku se zobrazí "
"sekce :icon:`fa-adjust` :guilabel:`Sammenligning`. Klikněte na jednu ze dvou "
"dostupných možností, buď :guilabel:`Startdato: Forrige periode`, "
"nebo :guilabel:`Startdato: Forrige år`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:59
msgid ""
"The report now displays three columns of information for every displayed "
"measure: a column for the current time period, a column for the previous "
"time period, and a :guilabel:`Variation` column, which displays the "
"difference between the two time periods in a color-coded percentage (green "
"for increases, red for decreases.)"
msgstr ""
"Přehled nyní zobrazuje tři sloupce informací pro každou zobrazenou metriku: "
"sloupec pro aktuální časové období, sloupec pro předchozí časové období a "
"sloupec :guilabel:`Variation`, který zobrazuje rozdíl mezi dvěma časovými "
"obdobími jako barevně rozlišené procento (zelená pro nárůst, červená pro "
"pokles)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:65
msgid ""
"In this example, the data shows an overall increase in the number of "
"payslips. Since the company pays all employees every two weeks, an increase "
"in the number of payslips (:guilabel:`# Payslips`) means that more employees "
"were hired, in this example, a 500% increase."
msgstr ""
"V tomto příkladu data ukazují celkový nárůst počtu lønsedler. Vzhledem k "
"tomu, že společnost vyplácí všem medarbejdere každé dva týdny, znamená "
"nárůst počtu lønsedler (:guilabel:`# Lønsedler`), že bylo přijato více "
"medarbejdere, v tomto případě nárůst o 500%."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:69
msgid ""
"Additionally, both the :guilabel:`Net Wage` and :guilabel:`Gross Wage` "
"increased. The department :guilabel:`RD US` showed the largest growth, with "
"both metrics increasing by approximately 350%."
msgstr ""
"Dále se zvýšila :guilabel:`Nettoløn` i :guilabel:`Bruttoløn`. "
"Afdeling :guilabel:`RD US` zaznamenala největší růst, přičemž obě metriky se "
"zvýšily přibližně o 350%."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:0
msgid "Pivot table view comparing two years of data."
msgstr "Zobrazení pivottabelu porovnávající dva roky dat."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:76
msgid ":doc:`../../essentials/reporting`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../essentials/reporting`"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations.rst:5
msgid "Payroll localizations"
msgstr "Lønlokaliseringer"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations.rst:10
msgid ""
"*Payroll localizations* refer to the specific process of adapting payroll "
"systems, policies, and compliance measures to align with the specific labor "
"laws, tax regulations, and social security requirements of a particular "
"country or region."
msgstr ""
"*Lønlokaliseringer* refererer til den specifikke proces med at tilpasse "
"lønsystemer, politikker og compliancetiltag, så de er i overensstemmelse med "
"de specifikke arbejdsretlige regler, skatteregler og sociale sikringskrav i "
"et bestemt land eller en bestemt region."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations.rst:14
msgid ""
"This ensures that employee salaries, benefits, deductions, and contributions "
"are processed accurately and in full compliance with local legal and "
"financial obligations."
msgstr ""
"Dette sikrer, at medarbejdernes lønninger, fordele, fradrag og bidrag "
"behandles nøjagtigt og i fuld overensstemmelse med lokale juridiske og "
"økonomiske forpligtelser."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations.rst:17
msgid ""
"Localization also includes integrating country-specific payroll elements "
"such as benefits, holidays, termination rules, and reporting requirements, "
"helping businesses avoid legal risks while ensuring employees receive their "
"correct compensation."
msgstr ""
"Lokalisering omfatter også integration af landespecifikke lønelementer som "
"fordele, helligdage, fratrædelsesregler og rapporteringskrav, hvilket "
"hjælper virksomheder med at undgå juridiske risici og sikre, at "
"medarbejderne modtager deres korrekte kompensation."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations.rst:22
msgid "Install localization package"
msgstr "Installer lokaliseringspakke"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations.rst:24
msgid ""
"A country-specific localization module :ref:`must be installed <general/"
"install>` to properly configure and process payroll. To install the required "
"module, first open the **Apps** app."
msgstr ""
"Et landespecifikt lokaliseringsmodul :ref:`skal være installeret <general/"
"install>` for at kunne konfigurere og behandle løn korrekt. For at "
"installere det krævede modul skal du først åbne appen **Apps**."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations.rst:27
msgid ""
"Clear out the default :icon:`fa-filter` :guilabel:`Apps` filter, then type "
"the name of the desired country into the search bar. All available modules "
"for that country are presented."
msgstr ""
"Ryd standardfilteret :icon:`fa-filter` :guilabel:`Apps`, og indtast derefter "
"navnet på det ønskede land i søgefeltet. Alle tilgængelige moduler for det "
"pågældende land vises."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations.rst:31
msgid ""
"Some countries only have one localization module, while other have multiple "
"modules. This is typically when other software is neede to process payroll, "
"and importing and exporting data is required."
msgstr ""
"Nogle lande har kun ét lokaliseringsmodul, mens andre har flere moduler. "
"Dette er typisk tilfældet, når anden software er nødvendig for at behandle "
"løn, og import og eksport af data er påkrævet."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations.rst:35
msgid ""
"For example. when searching for **Payroll** modules for `Egypt`, the "
"following modules appear in the search, and must be installed: `Egypt - "
"Payroll` and `Egypt - Payroll with Accounting`."
msgstr ""
"For eksempel vises følgende moduler i søgningen, når der søges efter "
"**Payroll**-moduler til `Egypten`, og de skal installeres: `Egypt - Payroll` "
"og `Egypt - Payroll with Accounting`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations.rst:38
msgid ""
"Refer to the :ref:`country-specific documentation <payroll_localizations/"
"countries-list>` for a complete list of the related **Payroll** modules "
"required for each specific country."
msgstr ""
"Se den :ref:`landespecifikke dokumentation <payroll_localizations/countries-"
"list>` for en komplet liste over de relaterede **Payroll**-moduler, der "
"kræves for hvert specifikt land."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations.rst:42
msgid ""
"To see if any localization modules have been installed on the database, "
"navigate to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> Configuration --> Settings`. In "
"the :guilabel:`Settings` page, if a localization module was installed, "
"a :guilabel:`(Country) Localization` section appears."
msgstr ""
"For at se, om der er installeret lokaliseringsmoduler på databasen, skal du "
"navigere til :menuselection:`Løn-app --> Konfiguration --> Indstillinger`. "
"På siden :guilabel:`Indstillinger` vises et afsnit med :guilabel:`(Land) "
"Lokalisering`, hvis et lokaliseringsmodul er blevet installeret."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations.rst:47
msgid ""
"It is **not** recommended to alter the localization settings, unless "
"specifically required."
msgstr ""
"Det anbefales **ikke** at ændre lokaliseringsindstillingerne, medmindre det "
"specifikt er påkrævet."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations.rst:50
msgid ""
"Odoo can handle a multi-company configuration. This is generally done when "
"there is a main company or office location, such as a headquarters, and "
"there are other offices/branches around the country or globe, that fall "
"under that main company or headquarters. In Odoo, each company, including "
"the headquarters, must be set up as their own company/branch using the multi-"
"company method."
msgstr ""
"Odoo kan håndtere en konfiguration med flere virksomheder. Dette gøres "
"generelt, når der er en hovedvirksomhed eller hovedkontor, og der er andre "
"kontorer/filialer rundt om i landet eller globalt, som hører under denne "
"hovedvirksomhed eller hovedkontor. I Odoo skal hver virksomhed, inklusive "
"hovedkontoret, oprettes som sin egen virksomhed/filial ved hjælp af metoden "
"til flere virksomheder."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations.rst:56
msgid ""
"Each individual company can have a different localization setting, since "
"locations can vary anywhere in the world, where rules and laws differ."
msgstr ""
"Hver enkelt virksomhed kan have en forskellig lokaliseringsindstilling, da "
"placeringer kan variere hvor som helst i verden, hvor regler og love er "
"forskellige."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations.rst:59
msgid ""
"For more information on companies, refer to the :doc:`Companies <../../"
"general/companies>` documentation, which covers how to set up companies."
msgstr ""
"For mere information om virksomheder henvises til dokumentationen "
"for :doc:`Virksomheder <../../general/companies>`, som dækker, hvordan "
"virksomheder oprettes."

