#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:90
msgid ""
"In May 2012, the :abbr:`ASIC (Australian Securities and Investments "
"Commission)` required businesses to register all names. From November 1, "
"2025 on, all unregistered trading names are retired from the :abbr:`ABR "
"(Australian Business Register)`, and businesses are required to register "
"their trading name as a business name."
msgstr ""
"I maj 2012 krævede :abbr:`ASIC (Australian Securities and Investments "
"Commission)`, at virksomheder skulle registrere alle navne. Fra den 1. "
"november 2025 udgår alle uregistrerede handelsnavne fra :abbr:`ABR "
"(Australian Business Register)`, og virksomheder skal registrere deres "
"handelsnavn som et virksomhedsnavn."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:95
msgid ""
":guilabel:`ABN`: Enter the company's eleven-digit :abbr:`ABN (Australian "
"Business Number)` in this field. After this is entered, "
"click :guilabel:`Verify ABN`, to ensure the number is correct."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`ABN`: Indtast virksomhedens tocifrede :abbr:`ABN (Australian "
"Business Number)` i dette felt. Efter indtastning skal du klikke på "
":guilabel:`Bekræft ABN` for at sikre, at nummeret er korrekt."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:97
msgid ""
":guilabel:`GST registered`: Select this checkbox if the company is "
"registered for Australian :abbr:`GST (Goods and Services Tax)`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`GST-registreret`: Marker dette afkrydsningsfelt, hvis "
"virksomheden er registreret til australsk :abbr:`GST (Goods and Services Tax)"
"`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:99
msgid ""
":guilabel:`ACN`: Enter the company's nine-digit :abbr:`ACN (Australian "
"Company Number)`. This number is issued by the :abbr:`ASIC (Australian "
"Securities and Investments Commission)`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`ACN`: Indtast virksomhedens nicifrede :abbr:`ACN (Australian "
"Company Number)`. Dette nummer udstedes af :abbr:`ASIC (Australian "
"Securities and Investments Commission)`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:101
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Currency`: By default, :abbr:`AUD (Australian Dollars)` is "
"selected. If not, select :guilabel:`AUD` from the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Valuta`: Som standard er :abbr:`AUD (Australian Dollars)` valgt. "
"Hvis ikke, skal du vælge :guilabel:`AUD` fra rullemenuen."

