#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/employment_hero.rst:52
msgid "How does the API work?"
msgstr "Jak funguje API?"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/employment_hero.rst:54
msgid ""
"The API syncs the journal entries from Employment Hero to Odoo and leaves "
"them in draft mode. The reference includes the Employment Hero payslip entry "
"ID in brackets for the user to easily retrieve the same record in Employment "
"Hero and Odoo."
msgstr ""
"API'en synkroniserer kladdeposterne fra Employment Hero til Odoo og "
"efterlader dem i kladdetilstand. Referencen inkluderer Employment Hero-"
"lønseddelpost-id'et i kantede parenteser, så brugeren nemt kan hente den "
"samme post i Employment Hero og Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/employment_hero.rst:None
msgid ""
"Example of a Employment Hero Journal Entry in Odoo Accounting (Australia)"
msgstr "Příklad položky deníku Employment Hero v Odoo Accounting (Austrálie)"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/employment_hero.rst:61
msgid ""
"By default, the synchronisation happens once per week. The records can be "
"fetched manually by going to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --"
"> Settings` and, in the :guilabel:`Enable Employment Hero Integration` "
"option, click on :guilabel:`Fetch Payruns Manually`."
msgstr ""
"Ve výchozím nastavení probíhá synchronizace jednou týdně. Záznamy lze načíst "
"ručně přechodem do :menuselection:`Regnskab --> Konfigurace --> Nastavení` a "
"v možnosti :guilabel:`Povolit integraci Employment Hero` klikněte "
"na :guilabel:`Načíst výplatní období ručně`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/employment_hero.rst:65
msgid ""
"Employment Hero payslip entries also work based on double-entry bookkeeping."
msgstr ""
"Položky výplatních pásek Employment Hero také fungují na základě podvojného "
"účetnictví."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/employment_hero.rst:67
msgid ""
"The accounts used by Employment Hero are defined in the "
"section :guilabel:`Payroll settings`."
msgstr ""
"Účty používané Employment Hero jsou definovány v sekci :guilabel:`Nastavení "
"mezd`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/employment_hero.rst:None
msgid "Chart of Accounts menu in Employment Hero"
msgstr "Menu Kontoplaner v Employment Hero"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/employment_hero.rst:72
msgid ""
"For the API to work, create the same accounts as the default accounts of the "
"Employment Hero business (**same name and same code**) in Odoo. The correct "
"account types must be chosen in Odoo to generate accurate financial reports."
msgstr ""
"Aby API fungovalo, vytvořte v Odoo stejné účty jako výchozí účty firmy "
"Employment Hero (**stejný název a stejný kód**). V Odoo musí být zvoleny "
"správné typy účtů pro generování přesných finančních sestav."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:5
msgid "Hong Kong"
msgstr "Hong Kong"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:10
msgid ""
"The Hong Kong payroll localization ensures all salary computations strictly "
"comply with the `Employment Ordinance (Cap. 57) <https://www.labour.gov.hk/"
"eng/legislat/content2.htm>`_ and `Inland Revenue Department (IRD) <https://"
"www.ird.gov.hk/eng/ese/erc.htm>`_ requirements. This includes automated "
"calculations for |MPF| contributions, the generation of IR56 reports, and "
"the processing of leave payments such as Payment in Lieu of Notice, "
"Severance Payments (SP), and Long Service Payments (LSP)—fully updated for "
"the 2025 |MPF| offsetting transition rules."
msgstr ""
"Hong Kong-lønlokalisering sikrer, at alle lønberegninger nøje overholder "
"`Employment Ordinance (Cap. 57) <https://www.labour.gov.hk/eng/legislat/"
"content2.htm>`_ og `Inland Revenue Department (IRD) <https://www.ird.gov.hk/"
"eng/ese/erc.htm>`_ kravene. Dette inkluderer automatiserede beregninger for |"
"MPF|-bidrag, generering af IR56-rapporter og behandling af fraværsbetalinger "
"såsom betaling i stedet for opsigelse, fratrædelsesgodtgørelse (SP) og "
"langvarig ansættelsesbetalinger (LSP) – fuldt opdateret til 2025 |MPF|-"
"modregningsovergangsreglerne."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:18
msgid ""
"Before configuring the Hong Kong localization, refer to the "
"general :doc:`payroll <../../payroll>` documentation. It covers foundational "
"information applicable to all localizations, including universal settings, "
"salary structures, and global payroll fields."
msgstr ""
"Før konfiguration af Hongkong-lokaliseringen skal du læse den "
"generelle :doc:`løn <../../payroll>`-dokumentation. Den dækker grundlæggende "
"information, der gælder for alle lokaliseringer, herunder universelle "
"indstillinger, lønstrukturer og globale lønfelter."

